{"tid":282713,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"[死渠頭訓嘰笠] EU超時任務 回帶討論區","createTime":"2017-06-13T14:57:28.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-17T23:34:25.000Z","uid":5313,"like":5,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"e0d874046e4f17faec733f5bfdc26d22875322c9","tid":282713,"uid":5313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-13T14:57:28.000Z","msg":"套劇已經播出左一年有多，岩先上Youtube發現新upload左幾段關於signal wong既新片，有幾段係eu剪出黎既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> D回憶即刻番哂黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔知仲有冇巴絲記得呢套劇，或者番煲，歡迎討論下<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=qxyCei9hKhI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DqxyCei9hKhI&d=%2FQqxfeiPpKxEeDMUAno1dJ4%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=20facde3\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=qxyCei9hKhI</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=yWhl-lWeL9I\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DyWhl-lWeL9I&d=%2FQqxfeiPpKxEeDMUAno1dJ4%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=38eb4fd9\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=yWhl-lWeL9I</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">播出日期:2016年3月21日-2016年4月10日 晚上9:30-10:30</span><br />\n<img src=\"http://fs.mingpao.com/ldy/20160411/s00009/1460373696136SF_AC83F73A2F8458BE37300434D55AEEF5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fldy%2F20160411%2Fs00009%2F1460373696136SF_AC83F73A2F8458BE37300434D55AEEF5.jpg&h=d24dc493&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://ww3.sinaimg.cn/large/6482e5f1gw1f2sw36nvn3g20j60as7wx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fww3.sinaimg.cn%2Flarge%2F6482e5f1gw1f2sw36nvn3g20j60as7wx.jpg&h=2dc9ff55&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://n2.hk/d/attachments/day_160418/20160418_00ffe940ddf5f82e2d3bmobAu0bKV0PQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fn2.hk%2Fd%2Fattachments%2Fday_160418%2F20160418_00ffe940ddf5f82e2d3bmobAu0bKV0PQ.jpg&h=f1f5dd07&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nMadam Ling：我有一段重複穿越三日嘅奇幻經歷，每次都由四月三日返到去四月一日，呢度係一個充滿變幻纷亂嘅地方，每個人都有自己嘅目標同期望，不同嘅穿越、不同嘅挑戰，帶俾我不斷嘅責任同任務，當維護使命同任務帶來痛苦、悲劇。我需要希望同奇蹟，憑著穿越奇蹟，我以為可以掌握一切，但係生命嘅變幻，又有邊個可以掌握得到。 <br />\n<br />\n渠頭：你地有冇試過應承一個人，你以後唔會離開佢但你做唔到呀？如果有一日個天同你講：你可以返轉頭，比機會你去彌補一切，你會點呀？起初你會覺得好興奮，因為所有野都係你掌握之內 ，但係最後你會發現，你重覆又重覆，你建立又破壞 ，原來只有你可以帶住你D回憶返去既話，你得到既，只有孤獨同永遠放唔低既痛苦。 <br />\n<br />\n命運　從不在手<br />\n但奇蹟　郤可尋找 <br />\n將來　也許可以改變 <br />\n但最美麗的原來早已在手 <br />\n緊緊擁抱　你所擁有 <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">死渠頭 </span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">訓嘰笠 </span></span>"},{"pid":"276a7a825ea2590335190444ce0ce4d35ef57d38","tid":282713,"uid":5313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-13T14:59:48.000Z","msg":"Over Run Over - EU超時任務 全集 <br />\n[url]<a href=\"http://dramacity.se/2016-hk-drama/over-run-over-eu超時任務/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fdramacity.se%2F2016-hk-drama%2Fover-run-over-eu%E8%B6%85%E6%99%82%E4%BB%BB%E5%8B%99%2F&d=%2FQqxfeiPpKxEeDMUAno1dJ4%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=b0696690\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://dramacity.se/2016-hk-drama/over-run-over-eu超時任務/</a> <br />\n[/url]<br />\n【EU超時任務 MV】王浩信 朱千雪 - 最真心一對 <br />\n<a href=\"http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=3h2QZjyAr2A\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D3h2QZjyAr2A&d=%2FQqxfeiPpKxEeDMUAno1dJ4%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=654a224e\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=3h2QZjyAr2A</a><br />\n<br />\n愛要及時 渠頭深情告白　《EU超催淚任務》結局精華 <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=68NUOEJnCis\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D68NUOEJnCis&d=%2FQqxfeiPpKxEeDMUAno1dJ4%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=d992755a\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=68NUO